Title: Rolex Oyster Perpetual Sky-Dweller Mens Automatic Watch 326138
Description: Watches Jewelry Accessories About us Policies Rolex Oyster Perpetual Sky-Dweller Mens Automatic Watch 326138 (Click to Enlarge) Rolex Oyster Perpetual Sky-Dweller Mens Automatic Watch 326138 Condition: Unworn Brand: Rolex Series: Sky-Dweller Retail Price: $38,150.00 Reference: 326138 Also Known As: 326138 Web ID: 150483Stock Number: 2187857Case Size: 42 mm Gender: Gents Movement: Automatic Bezel: 18K Yellow Gold Functions: Hours, Minutes, Seconds, Date, Second Time Zone Strap: Crocodile Clasp Type: Deployment Signatures: Rolex Included Items: Manufacturer's Papers Materials: 18K Yellow Gold Finishing: 18K Yellow Gold Case Back: Solid Dial Color: Silver The functions of this uniquely masculine Oyster Perpetual Sky-Dweller watch from Rolex are hours, minutes, seconds, date and second time zone. These functions are cleverly set out on a stylish silver dial that is enclosed in a fluted bezel. The articulately calibrated dial uses elegant luminescent hour and minute hands, a central needle-like seconds hand and Roman numeral hour markers to display local time in hours, minutes and seconds. For the GMT time zone display, an off-centered dial displays hours in 24-hour notation while minutes are displayed using a red rectangular indicator behind each Roman numeral hour marker. The dial also showcases a magnified rectangular date display at 3 o'clock and, as per modern Rolex tradition, the horologist's logo below 12 o'clock. The watch features a comfortable and durable brown crocodile leather and a round 42mm case made of 18K yellow gold.Please note that some watches are on memo from other dealers and do not carry a return policy, you will be notified before your purchase if the selected watch meets this criteria.
